{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">通过实验认识浮力</span></span><span style=\"font-family:'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">知道阿基米德原理。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">F</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浮</span></span></sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">=G</span><sub><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">排</span></span></sub></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">弹簧测力计、金属块、盛水烧杯、盛盐水烧杯、钩码</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">用测力计测出金属块所受的重力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2. <span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把被测物体浸没在盛满水的溢水杯中，读出这时测力计的示数。同时，用小桶收集物体排开的水。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测出小桶和物体排开的水所受的总重力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">测出小桶所受的重力。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">把测量的实验数据记录在表格中。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">根据实验数据，看看该物体所受的浮力跟它排开的水所受的重力有什么关系。</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">改换物体，重复实验，看看是否都存在这种关系。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浸在液体中的物体受到向上的浮力，浮力的大小等于它排开的液体所受的重力</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阿基米德原理：</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">浸在液体中的物体受到向上的浮力，浮力的大小等于它排开的液体所受的重力</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">阿基米德原理对于气体也是适用的。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}